<h2>
    Artistic Identity
</h2>
<p>
    I try to loosely base my style on Ace Attorney (the 2d ones) even though most of the specifics come from my method.
</p>
<p>
    I do sketches before going over the lines with a hard brush for a 'clean' aspect, I do colours on one or two layers and I apply between one and two levels of light and shade with extra details added with a soft brush.
</p>
<br>
